quran[31]{c,v,t}:
  76,1,"Rẽ yĩnga pa wa ninsaal zugẽ tɩ wakat n zĩnd tɩ yẽndµ rag n pa yɩ bũmb sẽn togsde?"
  76,2,"Tõnd naana ninsaal ne mani sẽn pul taaba, n zarbd-a, n maan-a t'a yaa wʋmd n yaa neta."
  76,3,"Tõnd vẽnega-la sorã, ma t'a yaa sõm-zɩta ma bark pʋʋsda."
  76,4,"Tõnd segla kɩfr-rãmbã yĩnga bãense, la gʋla, la bug-ziglga."
  76,5,"Ad nin-sõmbsã yũuda ne ko-teese, a gẽdgã yɩɩme n yaa Kaafʋʋre."
  76,6,"Yaa ko-nifr tɩ Wẽnd yembsã yũud ne-a, tɩ b wiid a wiib tεkẽ."
  76,7,"B pidsda b pʋlengã, la b leb n yaeesd raar ningɑ wẽngã sẽn gũbgã."
  76,8,"La b rɩlgd rɩɩb b nonglem zugu, ninbãan-dãmb la kɩɩbs la b sẽn yõg-b rãmb zab-laagẽ."
  76,9,"Tõnd sẽn rɩlgd yãmbã, yaa Wẽnd yĩnga, tõnd pa rat yaood yãmb nengẽ, pa bark pʋʋsg me."
  76,10,"Tõnd yaeesda d Soabã ning-gãneng raarã, keelem raarã."
  76,11,"Tɩ Wẽnd gũ-b ne ra-kãng raar wẽngã la a kɩt tɩ b seg neerem la sũ-noogo."
  76,12,"La a rol-b b sẽn maan sugrã yĩnga, Arzãn la Harɩɩr futu."
  76,13,"B yaa sẽn kɩl a pʋgẽ gaot zutu, b pa yãt wĩndg a pʋgẽ, pa wao-fugdg me."
  76,14,"A maasmã yaa sẽn pẽ bãmb zugu, la b zõneg a gĩinã zõnegr tεkẽ."
  76,15,"La b gilgda b zug ne laas sẽn yaa wanzurfu la ko-tees sẽn yaa wa nin-gεtga."
  76,16,"Nin-gεtg sẽn yaa wanzurfu, b mag-a-la magb tεkẽ."
  76,17,"La b yũnugd-b a pʋgẽ ko-tεεga, a gẽdgã yɩɩme n yaa zangabɩɩl (yãɑmɑku)."
  76,18,"Ko-nif n be a pʋgẽ tɩ b boon tɩ Salsabɩɩl."
  76,19,"Koamb n leb n gilgd b zug n yaa ruumdba, f sã n yã-ba, fo tẽed-b lame ne lʋʋ-lʋʋ (koomẽ sãnem) sẽn sãeege."
  76,20,"Fo sã n yã beenẽ, fo yã neema la naam sẽn bedme."
  76,21,"B yera fut sẽn yaa Sʋndʋs futu (fu-tagd sẽn bʋgse) la ɭstabrake (fu-faases sẽn bʋgse), la b faas-b ne zũy sẽn yaa wanzuri, tɩ f Soabã yũnug-b bõn-yũuds sẽn yaa yɩlgemde."
  76,22,"Ad wãndã yɩɩme n yaa rolb ne yãmba, yãmb tʋʋmã me yɩɩ b sẽn pʋʋsd barka."
  76,23,"Ad Tõnd sika Alkʋrãanã ne sikri."
  76,24,"Bɩ f maan sugr ne f Soabã bʋʋd la f ra wa n tũ b pʋgẽ zũnuub soab ma kɩfr ye."
  76,25,"La f tẽeg f Soabã Yʋʋr yibeoog la zaabre."
  76,26,"La yʋngã, bɩ f maan suguud A yĩngɑ la f yɩlg-A yʋʋrã yʋng sɑ-sɑ n wogle."
  76,27,"Ad bãmbã rãmb nonga yãgbã la b bas b poorẽ raar sẽn zɩse."
  76,28,"Tõnd n naan-ba la D keng b naanegã. La Tõnd sã n tʋll n nɑ n hlk-bɑ, D tedgd-b lɑ ne bãmb buudu tedgr tεkẽ."
  76,29,"Ad wãnde yaa tẽegre, ned ning sẽn tʋll-a bɩ a bao sor n tʋg a Soabã nengẽ."
  76,30,"La yãmb kõn tõoge, rallame tɩ Wẽnd sã n rata, ad Wẽnd yɩɩme n yaa mit n yaa yam bedr Soaba."
  76,31,"A kẽesda A sẽn rat-a A yolsgã pʋgẽ, la wẽgdbã A segla b yĩng naong sẽn zabde."
